{"lemma":"عِنِّينٌ","slug":"عِنِّينٌ","root":"ع.ن.ن","root_slug":"ع-ن-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ن-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30664"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%86%D9%90%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%86%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"impotent, frigid"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30664","headword_ar":"عِنِّينٌ","root":"En","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, * K, TA,) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiE~iylN","text_ar":"فِعِّيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaniynN","text_ar":"عَنِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [thus written in two places in the TA, and written without teshdeed in my copy of the Msb, but in the latter case app. from carelessness of the copyist, for otherwise the well-known form"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ein~iynN","text_ar":"عِنِّينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not there mentioned,] of which (i. e. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaniynN","text_ar":"عَنِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EununN","text_ar":"عُنُنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl., [which seems to show that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaniynN","text_ar":"عَنِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ein~iynN","text_ar":"عِنِّينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEulN","text_ar":"فُعُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a measure of a pl. of many epithets of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadiydN","text_ar":"جَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"na*iyrN","text_ar":"نَذِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., but not, to my knowledge, of any word of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiE~iylN","text_ar":"فِعِّيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (TA,) A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"incapable of going in to women;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb;) one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who does not go in to women by reason of impotence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, as some say, one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has connection with her who is not a virgin, but not with the virgin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is not desirous of women:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEonuwnN","text_ar":"مَعْنُونٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEan~N","text_ar":"مُعَنٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEan~anN","text_ar":"مُعَنَّنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) signify the same. (Msb, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ein~iynapN","text_ar":"عِنِّينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies A woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not desirous of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, * TA:) but there is disagreement in respect of the application of the epithet to a woman. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","K","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B9%D9%86%D9%8A%D9%86/","headword_ar":"عنين","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23434#0d3049","body_html":"<span>العنين: هو من لا يقدر على الجماع لمرض أو كبر سن، أو يصل إلى الثيب دون البكر.</span>"}]}}